Package: webScraperRcpp
Title: High-Performance Web Scraper with R and C++
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("George", "Boustany", , "george@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A robust web scraper combining R for interface and C++ via Rcpp 
    for high-performance data parsing, memory management, and network requests. 
    Features include dynamic content handling, retry logic, rate limiting, and 
    data export to R data.frames.
